Who: LORD ELDER, Elita, Straight Shot
Location: Ark - Command Center

> "SURE!!"said Elita with a big smile and waving her little tail and doing a
> childish Militar salute she ran towards Lord elder and said cheerfuly "Did
> you heard Lord Elder??? I was assinated to keep you safe!!!!"

Lord Elder smiled and chuckled lightly, "Of course Elita, we could
always use one more hand." He turned to face Elita and sit her in the
seat next to him, much like a  little co pilot or assistant,

Elder glanced back up at Straight Shot, "Are planning on following
your brother out there into the same dangers?"

(TAG)

Preston
